         <critic>Maitland McDonagh</critic>
      </review>
      <review>
         <snippet>The darker side of the story -- how the advent of pro surfing was taken as an act of cultural colonialism by some of the locals -- adds gravity to this otherwise lightweight, if amiable summer diversion.</snippet>
